    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. She\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really solid shape! I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the regular maintenance, so she\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today. It\u2019s a great, dependable car that\u2019s served me well, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love driving it just as much as I have. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
