    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-loved daily driver that balances performance with everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though closer inspection reveals the expected minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small hairline scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014nothing that detracts from its impressive curb appeal. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and strictly smoke-free; the leather seats show only light bolster wear consistent with careful use, and all powered components, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound. It has benefited from a recent full synthetic oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, confirming the engine pulls smoothly and the transmission shifts without hesitation. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest car that has been maintained regularly and is ready for its next owner to drive home with total confidence.",
      "price": 32500.0,
