      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies engineering integrity and sophisticated styling. This well-maintained specimen has been curated to ensure a seamless transition for its next proprietor, offering a refined driving experience and a commanding presence on the road. Every component has been evaluated to meet our rigorous professional standards, ensuring that performance remains both consistent and impressive. A premier choice for those who demand excellence without compromise.",
