    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2003 BMW M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual gearbox. This example is mechanically robust, with the critical rear subframe reinforcement already completed and the double-VANOS system recently overhauled to ensure optimal cam timing. The S54\u2019s individual throttle bodies provide exceptional throttle response, and the M-Variable differential remains tight. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve adjustment and a cooling system refresh with a high-flow water pump. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and the interior bolsters show light patina, the chassis dynamics and powertrain performance remain sharp. A technically sound E46 for the purist who values mechanical pedigree over concours perfection.",
